To install this script just put this folder anywhere (usr/local for example),
edit the mininagios.cron file and replace the 'pathotomiminagios' string with 
the path to the mininagios script, set the permissions as needed and place the
mininagios.cron file in the /etc/cron.d/ directory.

Edit the config file to set your parameters for the checks.

Enjoy it!

